item.description:
Join us for an evening of casual networking and dining with members of the WBOA. Our social events are less structured than our morning breakfast meetings, as there is no speaker, but it gives you the chance to connect with people on a deeper level, and build those all important business relationships!

Our event will start at 5:30 with a cash bar, followed by dinner at 6:30.

Our menu is as follows. Please note in your RSVP your choice of entree.

Salad with House Dressing

Choice of:

Eggplant Neapolitan
lightly battered and topped with alouette and provolone cheeses with marinara sauce,
served over linguini.

Redfish Nouvelle
Cal's signature dish, lightly blackened and topped with shrimp, scallops, leaf spinach,
and a Mornay sauce, and served with rice pilaf and jalapeno-spiced coleslaw

Apple Strudel and Ice Cream
